TS 提供一个完整的团体促销期” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/all-members-of-bts-renew-contracts-with-big-hit-music-3500954">与代理机构</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jungkook-reveals-december-enlist-letter-to-fans-bts-3547476">BTS 柾国透露他将于下个月入伍，致粉丝的分享信</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
